title: The History of Henry Esmond, Esq., A Colonel in the Service of Her Majesty Queen Anne
creator: William Makepeace Thackeray
description: LibriVox recording of The History of Henry Esmond, Esq., A Colonel in the Service of Her Majesty Queen Anne by William Makepeace Thackeray, read by Librivox volunteers. A classic Victorian novel and a historical novel rolled into one! Read about court and army life during the reign of Queen Anne - a story of Catholic - Protestant intrigue, and the party which aspired to the restoration of Bonny Prince Charlie. And, a good love story as well. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org M4B format available
